high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn left and walk over to the sink then turn to face it.
Put the bar of soap in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean bar of soap.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the counter.
Put the clean bar of soap on the front edge of the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap on the counter.

high_descs: Walk slightly to the right and turn left towards the bar of soap on the counter.
Pick up the bar of soap from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the front of the sink.
Put the bar of soap in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Walk slightly to the right again and turn left to face the counter.
Put the bar of soap on the front of the counter, to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned bar of soap on a counter top.

high_descs: walk right to face counter to right of sink
pick up pink bar of soap from counter
wash soap in sink, pick up soap from sink
walk right to face counter to right of sink
anns.task_desc: put washed soap bar on counter
